    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "The giant twenty-one passenger Douglas\nairliners operated by Northwest Airlines\nhave a total wing span of ninety-five feet\nand stand\nseventeen feet in height, with\na length of sixty-four feet. Each of these\nDouglas liners carries a crew of three,\nCaptain, First Officer and Stewardess. All\nstewardesses are registered nurses.\nPOST CARD\nPlace\n1 Cent\nStamp\nHere"
